text: Khouth is a surname. Notable people who carry this name: * Samuel Vincent Khouth, Canadian actor, voiced Edd a.k.a. Double D from Ed, Edd n Eddy * Gabe Khouth, Canadian actor, voiced Nicol Amalfi in Gundam SEED and portrayed Sneezy/Dr. Clark in the Once Upon a Time TV series Category:Surnames
